product designer commercial digital innovation
as a product designer on the commercial digital innovation team you will work closely with other designer strategist developer product manager business analyst and data scientist to further our understanding of how people and commercial business interact with their money you will identify opportunity for change ideate on concept advocate for the need of our customer and lead design from empathy to iteration to deliver human-centered solution to our associate and commercial customer
about the role
product designers at capital one have a passion for solving complex problem they are human-centered in their approach to design and feel comfortable advocating for user need they are curious and demonstrate a passion for learning they are capable of generating idea and prototyping concept that are anchored in research insight subject knowledge technology requirement and business goal they have an exuberant passion for the power of strategic design and an anything is possible mindset they take pride in their work and yet they have a humble approach they are able to contribute a a designer from end-to-end on project which mean they are comfortable a researcher data scientist strategist and designer they employ design thinking method to uncover insight that help inform design decision they are excellent communicator and feel comfortable presenting their design decision in front of colleague and stakeholder
in this role you will
- collaborate with business analyst product manager developer and design team on research activity strategy session ideation design and testing of new product concept
- build empathy and be an advocate for our customer through participation in human-centered research and design
- translate user need style guide and requirement into elegant solution for complex problem
- leverage analytics tool to measure success present opportunity and support decision-making
- utilize lean and agile methodology
- present research finding and design concept to designer and product partner
- be a leader and mentor youll challenge grow and mentor designer and contribute to fostering a collaborative team spirit
basic qualifications
- at least 3 year of experience with user experience ux design
preferred qualifications
- masters degree in design
- 7+ year of experience with user experience ux design
- 7+ year of experience designing digital product or omni-channel service
- 3+ year of experience with information architecture ia
- 3+ year of experience creating prototype
- front-end development knowledge
